➜头被砍掉的一瞬间，是头觉得肉身掉了，还是身体觉得头断了？
http://www.sohu.com/a/415329667_624188	23724
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200828/2d45fcaf304a4f738224b6f9738c6ee4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在古装剧里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人脸红心不跳的剧情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">往往是这一幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f90d64303c4a45968033fc794f7e1f6e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哀嚎声越拉越远</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼看着砍头高潮就要来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">镜头来个急刹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接切换成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
